Additional experiments for decentralized vs centralized search 1 Introduction

Additional experiments for decentralized vs centralized search Kabir Veitas (kabir@singularitynet.io) 2018-10-03 1 Introduction The following additional experiments were run in order to a bit better figure out the relationship that agent number and edge number plays in decentralized search and centralized search, keeping all other paramters equal. These experiments are: No. expermentId Comment 1 EXP09-04-01-13-AzAjTh Run time dependency on edge numbers (all other parameters the same); edge number is modulated by similarityConnectThreshold parameter 2 EXP09-04-11-00-zmNPzL Run time dependency on agent number (all other parameters the same) 3 EXP09-04-04-11-kvIbMs 800 agents simulation (repeating crashed one)
